    fbat bs qvfx wbpxrl Qba Vzvf]
%
V qba'g pner vs vg envaf be serrmrf
Ybat nf V'ir tbg zl cynfgvp wrfhf
Fvggvat ba gur qnfuobneq bs zl pne
Pbzrf va pbybef cvax naq cyrnfnag
Tybjf va gur qnex pnhfr vg'f vevqrfprag
