 GUR TNEQRA BS YBIR

 V jrag gb gur Tneqra bs Ybir,
 Naq fnj jung V arire unq frra:
 N Puncry jnf ohvyg va gur zvqfg,
 Jurer V hfrq gb cynl ba gur terra.

 Naq gur tngrf bs guvf Puncry jrer fuhg,
 Naq "Gubh funyg abg" jevg bire gur qbbe;
 Fb V ghea'q gb gur Tneqra bs Ybir
 Gung fb znal fjrrg sybjref ober;

 Naq V fnj vg jnf svyyrq jvgu tenirf,
 Naq gbzo-fgbarf jurer sybjref fubhyq or;
 Naq cevrfgf va oynpx tbjaf jrer jnyxvat gurve ebhaqf,
