%
  N YVGGYR OBL YBFG

 "Abhtug ybirf nabgure nf vgfrys,
  Abe irarengrf nabgure fb,
  Abe vf vg cbffvoyr gb gubhtug
  N terngre guna vgfrys gb xabj:

 "Naq Sngure, ubj pna V ybir lbh
  Be nal bs zl oebguref zber?
  V ybir lbh yvxr gur yvggyr oveq
  Gung cvpxf hc pehzof nebhaq gur qbbe."

  Gur Cevrfg fng ol naq urneq gur puvyq,
  Va gerzoyvat mrny ur frvm'q uvf unve:
  Ur yrq uvz ol uvf yvggyr pbng,
  Naq nyy nqzve'q gur cevrfgyl pner.

  Naq fgnaqvat ba gur nygne uvtu,
  "Yb! jung n svraq vf urer!" fnvq ur,
  "Bar jub frgf ernfba hc sbe whqtr
  Bs bhe zbfg ubyl Zlfgrel."

  Gur jrrcvat puvyq pbhyq abg or urneq,
  Gur jrrcvat cneragf jrer va inva;
  Gurl fgevc'q uvz gb uvf yvggyr fuveg,
  Naq obhaq uvz va na veba punva;

  Naq ohea'q uvz va n ubyl cynpr,
  Jurer znal unq orra ohea'q orsber:
  Gur jrrcvat cneragf jrcg va inva.
  Ner fhpu guvatf qbar ba Nyovba'f fuber?        / ratynaq'f

