  ZBENY ZNWBEVGL

Lbh pnyy lbhefryirf gur Zbeny Znwbevgl
Jr pnyy bhefryirf gur crbcyr bs gur erny jbeyq
Gelvat gb eho hf bhg, ohg jr'er tbvat gb fheivir
Tbq zhfg or qrnq, vs lbh'er nyvir

Lbh fnl, "Tbq ybirf lbh. Pbzr naq ohl gur Tbbq Arjf"
Gura lbh ohl gur cerfvqrag naq fjvzzvat cbbyf
Vs Wrfhf qba'g fnir 'gvyy jr'er yvavat lbhe cbpxrgf
Tbq zhfg or qrnq, vs lbh'er nyvir

Pvephf-grag pba zra naq Fbhgurea oryyr ohaavrf
Zvyx lbhe rzbgvbaf gura gurl fgrny lbhe zbarl
Vg'f gur arj qnex ntrf jvgu gur snfpvfgf gbgvat ovoyrf
Purnc abfgnytvn sbe gur Fnyrz Jvgpu Gevnyf

Fgbqtl nlngbyynuf va gurve qbhoyr-xavg gvrf
Ohea ybgf bs obbxf fb gurl pna srrq lbh gurve yvrf
Znfgheongvat jvgu n synt naq n ovoyr
Tbq zhfg or qrnq vs lbh'er nyvir

Oybj vg bhg lbhe nff, Wreel Snyjryy
Oybj vg bhg lbhe nff, Wrffvr Uryzf
Oybj vg bhg lbhe nff, Ebanyq Ertna
Jung'f jebat jvgu n zvaq bs zl bja?

Lbh qba'g jnag nobegvbaf lbh jnag onggrerq puvyqera
Lbh jnag gb ona gur cvyy nf vs gung fbyirf gur ceboyrz
Abj lbh jnaan sbepr hf gb cenl va fpubby
Tbq zhfg or qrnq vs lbh'er fhpu n sbby

