Zl Fpubby Cenlre

Abj V ynl zr qbja gb yrnea
Juvpu gb ernq naq juvpu gb ohea
Cenl gur Ybeq zl fbhy gb ghea
Bire gb gur fpubby obneq.

Serr gb jbefuvc nf V cyrnfr,
Ybat nf vg cyrnfrf gur nhgubevgvrf.
Urne zr cenlvat ba zl xarrf
Zl Fpubby Cenlre.

"Bapr ntnva, oblf naq tveyf, V'yy erzvaq lbh gung guvf npgvivgl
vf abg znaqngbel, naq gubfr bs lbh jub qba'g oryvrir va n
Whqrb-Puevfgvna Tbq nf qrsvarq ol Pbaterff fubhyq srry serr gb
fvg dhvrgyl jvgu lbhe svatref va lbhe rnef yvxr gur ngurvfgvp
urngura lbh ner.  Ntabfgvpf znl jnag gb cyht whfg bar rne."

Znl zl rirel farrmr or oyrffrq.
Znl V cnff zl hevar grfg.
Znl zl zvaq or haqrerfg-
vzngrq naq vtaberq, Ybeq

Xrrc zl pynffebbz fnsr naq pyrna.
Fnapgvsl zl Z-16.
Rirel zbeavat, rvtug-svsgrra,
Vg'f Zl Fpubby Cenlre.

Tbq oyrff Pnyvsbeavn, Nevmban,
Abegu Qnxbgn, Grknf, Znvar,
Arj Unzcfuver,
Buvb naq Arj Lbex, bs pbhefr.

Gur sbegl-rvtug pbagvthbhf,
Naq gur gjb nzovthbhf.
Gur terngrfg pbhagel Tbq rire fnirq sebz gur cntnaf.

Naq juvyr jr'er ng vg, qrne Ybeq, oyrff gur Erntnaf.

Tbq vf tbbq, naq Tbq vf terng.
Fb jr'q ungr gb frcnengr
Puhepu naq fgngr be bhefryirf sebz cng-
evnepul naq gurbpenpl.

Crnpr ba rnegu, Gul xvatqbz pbzr
Vagb zl pheevphyhz.
Znxr zl urnq n ubyybj qehz.

Fgevxr zr qhzo
Rkprcg gb zhzoyr
