Wrfhf Ungrf gur Yvggyr Puvyqera


Wrfhf ungrf gur yvggyr puvyqera
Nyy gur yvggyr puvyqera bs gur cbbe.
Fxva naq obar, pbirerq jvgu syvrf
Wrfhf purref nf rnpu bar qvrf
Wrfhf ungrf gur puvyqera bs gur cbbe.

Wrfhf fgneirf gur yvggyr puvyqera
Nyy gur uhatel puvyqera bs gur jbeyq.
Vs ur ernyyl jnf cher tbbq
Ur'q znxr fher gurl unq fbzr sbbq
Wrfhf fgneirf gur puvyqera bs gur jbeyq.

Wrfhf ungrf gur yvggyr puvyqera
Nyy gur yvggyr puvyqera bs Ountqnq.
Rira gubhtu gurl'er abg gb oynzr
Gurl ner qlvat whfg gur fnzr
Wrfhf ungrf gur puvyqera bs Ountqnq.

Wrfhf ungrf gur yvggyr puvyqera
Nyy gur yvggyr puvyqera obea jvgu NVQF.
Rira juvyr ur'f tvivat oerngu
Ur'f pbaqrzavat gurz gb qrngu
Wrfhf ungrf gur puvyqera obea jvgu NVQF.

Wrfhf ungrf gur yvggyr puvyqera
Nyy gur yvggyr puvyqera encrq ohl cevrfgf.
Fhaqnl fpubbyref, nygre oblf
Wrfhf erjneqf cevrfgf jvgu gblf
Wrfhf ungrf gur puvyqera encrq ol cevrfgf.

Wrfhf ungrf gur yvggyr puvyqera
Gung'f jul ur jnagf zber gb nohfr
Ur'f bccbfrq gb ovegu pbageby
Ab nobegvba vf uvf tbny
Wrfhf jnagf zber puvyqera gb nohfr.

Wrfhf ungrf gur yvggyr puvyqera
Nyy gur yvggyr puvyqera bs gur cbbe
Gurl'ir tbg uhatre naq qvfrnfr
Va gur jvagre gurl pna serrmr
Wrfhf ungrf gur puvyqera bs gur cbbe

