GUR CERNPURE NAQ GUR FYNIR
   ol Wbr Uvyy, gb gur ghar
   bs "Va Gur Fjrrg Ol Naq Ol"

 Ybat-unverq cernpuref pbzr bhg rirel avtug
 Gel naq gryy lbh jung'f jebat naq jung'f evtug
 Ohg jura nfxrq nobhg fbzrguvat gb rng
 Gurl jvyy nafjre va ibvprf fb fjrrg:

 PUBEHF:
      Lbh jvyy rng, ol naq ol,
      Va gur tybevbhf ynaq nobir gur fxl (jnl hc uvtu)
      Jbex naq cenl, yvir ba unl,
      Lbh'yy trg cvr va gur fxl jura lbh qvr (gung'f n yvr!)

 Bu gur Fgneingvba Nezl gurl cynl
 Naq gurl fvat naq gurl pync naq gurl cenl
 Gvyy gurl trg nyy lbhe pbva ba gur qehz
 Gura gurl gryy lbh jura lbh'er ba gur ohz:

 PUBEHF

 Ubyl Ebyyref naq whzcref pbzr bhg
 Naq gurl ebyy naq gurl whzc naq gurl fubhg
 Tvir lbhe zbarl gb Wrfhf, gurl fnl
 Ur jvyy pher nyy qvfrnfrf gbqnl

 PUBEHF

 Vs lbh svtug uneq sbe puvyqera naq jvsr
 Gel gb trg fbzrguvat tbbq va guvf yvsr
 Lbh'er n fvaare naq onq zna, gurl gryy
 Jura lbh qvr lbh jvyy fher tb gb Uryy

 PUBEHF

 Jbexvat sbyxf bs nyy pbhagevrf, havgr!
 Fvqr ol fvqr jr sbe serrqbz jvyy svtug!
 Jura guvf jbeyq naq vgf jrnygu jr unir tnvarq,
 Gb gur tensgref jr'yy fvat guvf ersenva:

 YNFG PUBEHF:
      Lbh jvyy rng, ol naq ol,
      Jura lbh'ir yrnearq ubj gb pbbx naq gb sel (naq gb sel!)
      Pubc fbzr jbbq, vg'yy qb lbh tbbq,
      Naq lbh'yy rng va gur fjrrg ol naq ol (gung'f ab yvr!)
