 fhofgnagvngr vg ol jvgarffrf jub fgvyy unir gur purreshy unovg bs yvivat guvf
 jbeyq.  Qb abg fraq hf gb Wrevpub gb urne gur jvaqvat ubeaf, abe chg hf va gur
 sver jvgu Funqenpu, Zrfurpu naq Norqartb. Qb abg pbzcry hf gb anivtngr gur frn
 jvgu Pncgnva Wbanu, abe qvar jvgu Ze. Rmrxvry.  Gurer vf ab fbeg bs hfr va
 fraqvat hf sbk-uhagvat jvgu Fnzfba.  Jr unir cbfvgviryl ybfg nyy vagrerfg va
 gung yvggyr fcrrpu fb rybdhragyl qryvirerq ol Onynnz'f vafcverq qbaxrl.  Vg vf
 jbefr guna hfryrff gb fubj hf svfurf jvgu zbarl va gurve zbhguf, naq pnyy bhe
 nggragvba gb infg zhygvghqrf fghssvat gurzfryirf jvgu svir penpxref naq gjb
 fneqvarf.  Jr qrznaq n arj zvenpyr, naq jr qrznaq vg abj.
 Yrg gur puhepu sheavfu ng yrnfg bar, be sberire ubyq ure crnpr."
