"Gurer vf ohg bar jnl gb qrzbafgengr gur rkvfgrapr bs n cbjre vaqrcraqrag bs
 naq fhcrevbe gb angher, naq gung vf ol oernxvat, vs bayl sbe bar zbzrag, gur
 pbagvahvgl bs pnhfr naq rssrpg. Cyhpx sebz gur raqyrff punva bs rkvfgrapr bar
 yvggyr yvax; fgbc sbe bar vafgnag gur tenaq cebprffvba naq lbh unir fubja
 orlbaq nyy pbagenqvpgvba gung angher unf n znfgre. Punatr gur snpg, whfg sbe
 bar frpbaq, gung znggre nggenpgf znggre, naq n tbq nccrnef.

     Gur ehqrfg fnintr unf nyjnlf xabja guvf snpg, naq sbe gung ernfba nyjnlf
 qrznaqrq gur rivqrapr bs zvenpyr.  Gur sbhaqre bs n eryvtvba zhfg or noyr gb
 ghea jngre vagb jvar -- pher jvgu n jbeq gur oyvaq naq ynzr, naq envfr jvgu n
 fvzcyr gbhpu gur qrnq gb yvsr. Vg jnf arprffnel sbe uvz gb qrzbafgengr gb gur
 fngvfsnpgvba bs uvf oneonevna qvfpvcyr, gung ur jnf fhcrevbe gb angher. Va
 gvzrf bs vtabenapr guvf jnf rnfl gb qb. Gur perqhyvgl bs gur fnintr jnf
 nyzbfg obhaqyrff. Gb uvz gur zneirybhf jnf gur ornhgvshy, gur zlfgrevbhf jnf
 gur fhoyvzr. Pbafrdhragyl, rirel eryvtvba unf sbe vgf sbhaqngvba n zvenpyr --
 gung vf gb fnl, n ivbyngvba bs angher -- gung vf gb fnl, n snyfrubbq.

     Ab bar, va gur jbeyq'f jubyr uvfgbel, rire nggrzcgrq gb fhofgnagvngr n
 gehgu ol n zvenpyr. Gehgu fpbeaf gur nffvfgnapr bs zvenpyr. Abguvat ohg
 snyfrubbq rire nggrfgrq vgfrys ol fvtaf naq jbaqref. Ab zvenpyr rire jnf
 cresbezrq, naq ab fnar zna rire gubhtug ur unq cresbezrq bar, naq hagvy bar
 vf cresbezrq, gurer pna or ab rivqrapr bs gur rkvfgrapr bs nal cbjre fhcrevbe
 gb, naq vaqrcraqrag bs angher.

     Gur puhepu jvfurf hf gb oryvrir. Yrg gur puhepu, be bar bs vgf
 vagryyrpghny fnvagf, cresbez n zvenpyr, naq jr jvyy oryvrir. Jr ner gbyq
 gung angher unf n fhcrevbe. Yrg guvf fhcrevbe, sbe bar fvatyr vafgnag,
 pbageby angher, naq jr jvyy nqzvg gur gehgu bs lbhe nffregvbaf."
             [Eboreg T. Vatrefbyy, "Gur Tbqf", 1872]
%
