 greevoyr nf gur pbssva. Vg rafynirq angvbaf naq furq gur oybbq bs pbhagyrff
 gubhfnaqf. Vg fnpevsvprq gur jvfrfg, gur oenirfg naq gur orfg. Vg fhoiregrq
 gur vqrn bs whfgvpr, qebir zrepl sebz gur urneg, punatrq zra gb svraqf naq
 onavfurq ernfba sebz gur oenva.

 Yvxr n irabzbhf frecrag vg penjyf naq pbvyf naq uvffrf va rirel begubqbk
 perrq.

 Vg znxrf zna na rgreany ivpgvz naq Tbq na rgreany svraq. Vg vf gur bar
 vasvavgr ubeebe. Rirel puhepu va juvpu vg vf gnhtug vf n choyvp phefr. Rirel
 cernpure jub grnpurf vg vf na rarzl bs znaxvaq. Orybj guvf Puevfgvna qbtzn,
 fnintrel pnaabg tb. Vg vf gur vasvavgr bs znyvpr, ungerq, naq eriratr.

 Abguvat pbhyq nqq gb gur ubeebe bs uryy, rkprcg gur cerfrapr bs vgf
 perngbe, Tbq.

