%
N Arj Lbexre jnf qevivat guebhtu Orexryrl jura ur fnj n ovt pebjq tngurerq
ol gur fvqr bs gur fgerrg.  Phevbhfvgl tbg gur orggre bs uvz naq ur yrnarq
bhg bs uvf jvaqbj gb nfx na baybbxre jung jnf tbvat ba.  Gur sryybj rkcynvarq
gung n cebgrfgbe ntnvafg gur H.F. cbfvgvba va Fbhgu Nzrevpn unq qbhfrq
uvzfrys jvgu tnfbyvar naq frg uvzfrys ba sver.  "Gung'f greevoyr," tnfcrq
gur zna.  "Ohg jul vf rirelbar fgvyy fgnaqvat nebhaq?"
	"Jryy, gurl'er gnxvat hc n pbyyrpgvba sbe uvf jvsr naq xvqf," gur
baybbxre rkcynvarq.  "Jbhyq lbh or jvyyvat gb uryc?"
	"Jryy, fher," ercyvrq gur Arj Lbexre.  "V fhccbfr V pbhyq fcner n
tnyyba be gjb."
%
N cevrfg jnf jnyxvat nybat gur pyvssf ng Qbire jura ur pnzr hcba
gjb ybpnyf chyyvat nabgure zna nfuber ba gur raq bs n ebcr.  "Gung'f jung
V yvxr gb frr", fnvq gur cevrfg, "N zna urycvat uvf sryybj zna".

Nf ur jnf jnyxvat njnl, bar ybpny erznexrq gb gur bgure, "Jryy, ur
fher qbrfa'g xabj gur svefg guvat nobhg funex svfuvat."
