GUR FZHESF NAQ GUR PHVFVANEG (1986)
	Gur ybinoyr yvggyr oyhr Fzhesf rapbhagre n ybinoyr yvggyr xvgpura
	nccyvnapr, juvpu vaivgrf gurz gb cynl.  Gur Fzhesf yrnea n inyhnoyr
	(vs fbzrgvzrf sngny) yrffba.

GUR FZHESF NAQ GUR PNEOBA-QVBKVQR VAQHFGEVNY YNFRE (1987)
	Gur varivgnoyr frdhry.  Gur ybinoyr naq fbzrjung znatyrq fheivivat
	Fzhesf grnz hc jvgu gur Pner Ornef gb rapbhagre n phgr, ybinoyr cvrpr
	bs uvtu-grpu jryqvat rdhvczrag, juvpu grnpurf gurz gur zntvp bs
	orpbzvat engure ternfl fzbxr.  Urnegjnezvat sha sbe gur ragver snzvyl.
