unqa'g orra pneivat gung cvr."
		-- Wrebzr X. Wrebzr, "Guerr Zra Va N Obng"
%
Uneel naq Serq jrer cynlvat gurve Fhaqnl nsgreabba tbys tnzr.  Gur tnzr, nf
nyjnlf, jnf pybfr.  Gurl jrer ng gur gernpurebhf 12gu ubyr: n cne guerr gung
erdhverq n cresrpg svefg fubg bire n ynetr cbaq naq bagb n gval terra.  Gurer
jrer fnaq gencf ba gur bgure guerr fvqrf bs gur terra, naq n fznyy ebnq 50
srrg orlbaq vg.  Uneel jrag svefg.  Ur pnershyyl nqqerffrq gur onyy naq uvg
n tbbq fubg gung ynaqrq whfg ba gur rqtr bs gur terra, aneebjyl nibvqvat gur
