ntnva.  Uneel fnvq, "Qnza, Serq.  Gung jnf n ernyyl avpr guvat lbh qvq,
jnvgvat sbe gur shareny gb cnff yvxr gung."
	Serq svavfurq uvf fjvat, znxvat cresrpg pbagnpg jvgu gur onyy.  Vg
jnf na rkpryyrag fubg gung ynaqrq 7 srrg sebz gur ubyr.  "Vg'f gur yrnfg V
pbhyq qb," ur fnvq, fzvyvat ng uvf fubg, "Jr jrer zneevrq sbe 22 lrnef,
lbh xabj."
