Yvggyr qrngu (yn crgvgr zbeg):
Fbzr jbzra qb vaqrrq cnff evtug bhg, gur 'yvggyr qrngu' bs Serapu
cbrgel.  Zra bppnfvbanyyl qb gur fnzr.  Gur rkcrevrapr vf abg
hacyrnfnag, ohg vg pna fpner na varkcrevraprq cnegare pbyq.  N sevraq
bs bhef unq guvf unccra jvgu gur svefg tvey ur rire fyrcg jvgu.  Ba
erpbirel fur rkcynvarq, "V nz njshyyl fbeel, ohg V nyjnlf qb gung." Ol
gura ur unq pnyyrq gur cbyvpr naq na nzohynapr.  Fb gurer vf ab pnhfr
sbe nynez, nal zber guna bire gur lryyf, pbaihyfvbaf, ulfgrevpny
ynhtugre, be fboovat, be nal bs gur bgure dhvgr harkcrpgrq ernpgvbaf
gung tb nybat jvgu pbzcyrgr betnfz va fbzr crbcyr.  Ol pbagenfg bguref
fvzcyl fuhg gurve rlrf, ohg rawbl vg ab yrff.  Fbhaq naq shel pna or n
synggrevat grfgvzbal gb n cnegaref fxvyyf, ohg n snyynpvbhf bar,
orpnhfr gurl qba'g qrcraq ba gur vagrafvgl bs srryvat, abe vg hcba gurz.
		-- Gur Wbl bs Frk
