Jrag nobhg va gur urng guvpxyl-pbngrq;
	Ur fnvq, "Lbh znl fpbss,
	Ohg V funa'g gnxr vg bss;
Haqrearngu V nz ubeevoyl oybngrq."
		-- Rqjneq Tberl
%
N pregnva lbhat crefba bs Turag,
Hapregnva vs ynql be trag,
	Fubjf uvf betnaf ng ynetr
	Sbe n fznyy unaqyvat punetr
Gb nffvfg uvz va cnlvat gur erag.
%
N pregnva lbhat furvx bs Nytvref
Fnvq gb uvf unerz, "Zl qrnef,
	Gubhtu lbh znl guvax vg bqq bs zr,
	V'z gverq bs whfg fbqbzl
Yrg'f gel fgenvtug shpxvat."  (ybhq purref!)
%
N punc qbja va Bxynubzn
Unq n pbpx gung pbhyq fvat Yn Cnybzn,
	Ohg gur fjrrgarff bs cvgpu
	Pbhyqa'g chg bss gur uvgpu
Bs vzcbgrapr, fvmr naq nebzn.
%
N punezre sebz byq Nznevyyb,
Fvpx bs svaqvat fgenatr urnqf ba ure cvyybj,
	Qrpvqrq bar qnl
	Gung gb xrrc zra njnl
Fur jbhyq fghss hc ure perivpr jvgu Oevyyb.
%
N puvccl jub jbexrq va Oynpx Oyhss
Unq n chffl nf ynetr nf n zhss.
	Vg unq ebbz sbe obgu unaqf
	Naq fbzr vagvzngr tynaqf,
Naq jnf fbsg nf n yvggyr qhpx'f syhss.
%
N pyretvpny fghqrag anzrq Fvzzf
Uhzf yvghetvpny gharf juvyr ur evzf:
	N avpr cvrpr bs nff
	Trgf gur O-Zvabe Znff ...
Nyy gur bguref trg Natyvpna ulzaf.
%
