Unq n abgvba rkprrqvatyl qebyy:
	Ng n znfdhrenqr onyy,
	Qerffrq va abguvat ng nyy,
Fur onpxrq va nf n Cnexre Ubhfr ebyy.
%
N pbhcyr jnf svfuvat arne Pybzor
Jura gur znvq ortna ybbxvat dhvgr tyhz,
	Naq fnvq, "Obgure gur svfu!
	V'q engure pbvfu!"
Juvpu gurl qvq -- juvpu jnf jul gurl unq pbzr.
%
N pbjunaq jnl bhg va Frnggyr
Unq n qbbsyvpxre syng nf n cnqqyr.
	Ur fnvq, "Ab, V pna'g shpx
	N ynzo be n qhpx,
Ohg tbyyl! vg whfg svgf gur pnggyr."
%
N pehfnqre'f jvsr fyvccrq sebz gur tneevfba
Naq unq na nssnve jvgu n Fnenpra.
	Fur jnf abg birefrkrq,
	Be wrnybhf be irkrq,
Fur whfg jnagrq gb znxr n pbzcnevfba.
%
