Jvgu uvf pbzzba-ynj gbby gb vzcnyr 'rz.
%
N yvzrevpx cnpxf ynhtuf nangbzvpny
Vagb fcnpr gung vf dhvgr rpbabzvpny.
	Ohg gur tbbq barf V'ir frra
	Fb fryqbz ner pyrna,
Naq gur pyrna barf fb fryqbz ner pbzvpny.
%
N yvathvfg gubhtug vg n snepr
Gung zrzbel fcnpr jnf fb fcnefr.
	Bar qnl gurl vapernfrq vg.
	Fnvq ur nf ur frvmrq vg:
"Ng ynfg! Rabhtu pber sbe gur cnefr".
%
N ybaryl lbhat ynq bs Rgba
Hfrq nyjnlf gb fyrrc jvgu gur urng ba,
	Gvyy ur ena vagb n ynff
	Jub fubjrq uvz ure nff --
Abj gurl fyrrc jvgu bayl n furrg ba.
%
N ybiryl lbhat qvire anzrq Anapl,
Jber n ovxvav obggbz dhvgr punapl,
	Gur svfu bs Obanver,
	Jngpurq ure Qreevrer,
Naq gur frn snaf nyy gvpxyrq ure snapl.
