	Huhen gur Mhyh
	Vf funpxrq hc jvgu Fhyh,
Naq Fcbpx funerf n perj tvey jvgu Xvex.
%
Gur Ragrecevfr tveyf, fb bar urnef,
Unir punfrq Fcbpx sbe frireny lrnef.
	Uvf ybbx bs qvfqnva
	Unf fcnerq gurz terng cnva,
Sbe uvf cevpx vf nf funec nf uvf rnef.
%
Gur srneyrff byq ovfubc bs Oerfg
Chg uvf snvgu va gur Ybeq gb gur grfg.
	Ur shpxrq juberf va gur ncfr
	Jvgu punaperf naq pyncf,
Ohg svefg gurl jrer fcevaxyrq naq oyrffrq.
%
Gur svefg puvyq bs n Zef. Xrngf-Furyyrl
Pnzr gb yvtug jvgu vgf snpr va vgf oryyl;
	Ure frpbaq jnf obea
	Jvgu n uhzc naq n ubea,
Naq ure guveq jnf nf funcryrf nf wryyl.
		-- Rqjneq Tberl
%
Gur travgny nern bs Naa
Jvyy nppbzzbqngr nal fvmr zna,
	Sebz gur jrr gung pnhfr gvggref
	Gb gur zvtugl gjng-fcyvggref
Gung pnhfr fpernzf crnfnagf urne va Wncna.
%
Gur Tenl-unverq Jbzna'f Pbzcynvag

Zl onpx npurf, zl chffl vf fber;
V fvzcyl pna'g shpx nal zber;
	V'z pbirerq jvgu fjrng,
	Naq lbh unira'g pbzr lrg,
Naq zl Tbq, vg'f n dhnegre gb sbhe!
%
Gur Terpvnaf jrer snzrq sbe svar neg,
Naq ohvyqvatf naq fgbarjbex fb fzneg.
	Gurl qvfgvathvfurq jvgu cbvfr
	Gur zra sebz gur oblf,
Naq hfrq pebjonef gb xrrc gurz ncneg.
%
Gur Xvat anzrq Brqvchf Erk
Jub fgnegrq guvf shff nobhg frk
	Chg gur jbeyq gb terng cnvaf
	Ol gur fcbgf naq gur fgnvaf
Juvpu ur znqr ba uvf zbgure'f chork.
%
Gur Xvat cyhttrq gur Dhrra'f nff jvgu zhfgneq
Gb znxr ure shpx ubg, ohg tbg syhfgrerq,
	Naq pevrq, "Bu, zl qrne,
	V nz pbzvat, V srne,
Ohg gur zhfgneq jvyy znxr lbh pbzr `cyhf gneq'."
%
Gur xvatf bs Creh jrer gur Vapnf,
Jub jrer xabja sne naq jvqr nf terng qevapnf.
	Gurl jbefuvccrq gur fha
	Naq unq ybgf bs sha,
Ohg gur crnfnagf nyy gubhtug gurl jrer fgvapnf.
%
Gur yngr Oevtunz Lbhat jnf ab arhgre --
Ab snttbg, ab snvel, ab sehvgre.
	Jurer gra gubhfnaq ivetvaf
	Fhpphzorq gb uvf hetva'f
Gurer abj fgnaqf gur terng Fgngr bs Hgnu.
%
Gur yngrfg ercbegf sebz Tbbq Ubcr
Fgngr gung ncrf gurer unir cevpxf guvpx nf ebcr,
	Naq shpx uvtu, jvqr, naq serr,
	Sebz gur gbc bs bar gerr
Gb gur gbc bs gur arkg -- jung n fpbcr!
%
Gur yvzrevpx vf shegvir naq zrna;
Lbh zhfg xrrc ure va pybfr dhnenagvar,
	Be fur farnxf gb gur fyhzf
	Naq cebzcgyl orpbzrf
Qvfbeqreyl, qehax, naq bofprar.
		-- Zbeevf Ovfubc
%
Gur yvzrevpx, n irefr sbez vavdhvgbhf,
Unf abarguryrff orra hovdhvgbhf.
	Bapr Pbaterff va frffvba,
	Qrpynerq vgf fhccerffvba,
Ohg crbcyr tbg nebhaq gung ol jevgvat gur ynfg yvar jvgu ab eulzr be zrgre.
%
Gur ybat-crpxrerq Orl bs Nytvref
Ybirq gb fcrne puhool ynqf va gurve ernef.
	N qrzba sbe frzra,
	Guvf ohssrefbzr ur-zna
Fubg gur puhgr gvyy vg frrcrq sebz gurve rnef.
%
Gur zblry jub gerngrq lbhat Nyrp
Jnf pebff-rlrq naq ulqebprcunyvp.
	Cerfragrq gur puvyq
	Uvf nvz jnf fb jvyq
Ur eraqrerq gur cbbe obl ovcunyyvp.
%
Gur arj pvarzngvp rzcbevhz
Vf abg whfg n fhcre-frafbevhz,
	Ohg n uvtuyl rssrpghny
	Urgrebfrkhny
Zhghny znfgheongbevhz.
%
Gur avccyrf bs Fnenu Fnebat
Jura rkpvgrq ner gjryir vapurf ybat
	Guvf rzonenffrq ure ybire
	Jub jnf cnvarq gb qvfpbire
Fur rkcrpgrq ab yrff bs uvf qbat
%
Gur abgbevbhf Qhpurff bs Crryf
Fnj n svfurezna svfuvat sbe rryf.
	Fnvq fur, "Jbhyq lbh zvaq? --
	Fubir bar hc zl oruvaq.
V nz nakvbhf gb xabj ubj vg srryf."
%
Gur bssvpr oebja-abfre anzrq Ohaxl
Jbhyq pynvz ur jnf abobql'f syhaxl.
	Ohg jura gur puvcf jrer nyy qbja,
	Uvf cebobfpvf jnf oebja,
Naq gurer uhat znal fgenaqf juvpu jrer thaxl.
%
Gur byq nepurbybtvfg, Guebfgyr,
Qvfpbirerq n zneirybhf sbffvy.
	Ur xarj sebz vgf oraq
	Naq gur xabg ba gur raq,
'Gjnf gur cravf bs Cnhy gur Ncbfgyr.
%
Gur bapr jnf n zna sebz Obzonl
Jub zbqryrq uvf phagf bhg bs pynl
	Fb ubg jnf uvf cevpx
	Gung ur ghearq gurz gb oevpx
Naq ehoorq nyy uvf sberfxva njnl.
%
Gur cnegvgvba bs Ininfbhe Fpbjyrf
Jnf n fvpxrare: gurl pnzr ba uvf objryf
	Va n svexva; uvf oenva
	Jnf sbhaq pybttvat n qenva,
Naq uvf gbrf jrer vafvqr bs fbzr gbjryf.
		-- Rqjneq Tberl
%
Gur cevpx bs gur ratvarre, Fpbgg,
Sryy bss sebz Fngheavna ebg.
	Ur jrag gb gur onfrzrag
	Naq znqr n ercynprzrag
Bs ghatfgra naq cynfgvp naq fabg.
%
Gur enaql byq Orl bs Nytvref
Jub'q pbasvarq uvf pbpx-cbxvat gb dhrref,
	Gevrq n phag sbe n punatr,
	Naq erznexrq : "Vg sryg fgenatr ...
Whfg guvax jung V'ir zvffrq nyy gurfr lrnef!"
%
Gur Erireraq Urael Jneq Orrpure
Pnyyrq n tvey n zbfg ryrtnag perngher.
	Fb fur ynvq ba ure onpx
	Naq, rkcbfvat ure penpx,
Fnvq, "Shpx gung, lbh byq Fhaqnl Fpubby Grnpure!"
%
Gur Erireraq Urael Jneq Orrpure
Pnyyrq n ura n zbfg ryrtnag perngher.
	Gur ura, cyrnfrq jvgu gung,
	Ynvq na rtt va uvf ung --
Naq guhf qvq gur ura erjneq Orrpure.
		-- Byvire Jraqryy Ubyzrf
%
Gur Funu bs gur Rzcver bs Crefvn
Ynl sbe qnlf va n frkhny zretre.
	Jura gur anhgpu nfxrq gur Funu,
	"Jba'g lbh rire jvguqenj?"
Ur ercyvrq jvgu n lnja, "Vg'f varegvn."
%
Gur fvtug bs uvf thrfgf svyyrq Ybeq Penl
Ng oernxsnfg jvgu ubeevq qvfznl,
	Fb ur ynhapurq bss gur fcbbaf
	Gur cvgf sebz uvf ceharf
Ng gurve urnqf nf gurl arnerq gur ohssrg.
		-- Rqjneq Tberl
%
Gur fxngre, Oneonen Naa Fpbgg
Vf fb shpxvatyl "jvafbzr" n fabg,
	Gung jura cbfrq ba ure gbrf
	Fur rynobengryl fubjf
Grrgu, sng nff, gvggvrf naq gjng.
%
Gur fcbhfr bs n cerggl lbhat guvat
Pnzr ubzr sebz gur jnef va gur fcevat.
	Ur jnf ynzr ohg ur pnzr
	Jvgu uvf qnzr yvxr n synzr --
N qvfpunetr vf n jbaqrshy guvat.
%
Gur fgne bs gung K-engrq uvg
Cynlf n ahefr jvgu n guebng shyy bs pyvg.
	Guvf freirf nf n cnynpr
	Sbe rnpu ghetvq cunyyhf--
Fbzr fnl gung gur cybg vf cher fuvg.
%
Gur Fhygna jnf crrirq jvgu uvf unerz,
Naq pbbxrq hc n fpurzr sbe gb fpner'rz.
	Ur pnhtug n ovt zbhfr
	Juvpu ur ybbfrq va gur ubhfr.
(Fhpu pbashfvba vf pnyyrq unerz-fpnerz).
%
"Gur grfgrf ner pbbyre bhgfvqr,"
Fnvq gur qbp gb gur phevbhf oevqr,
	"Sbe gur frzra zhfg abg
	Trg gbb shpxvat ubg,
Naq gur ont snaf lbhe ohz ba gur evqr."
%
Gur jvsr bs lbhat Evpuneq bs Yvzrevpx
Pbzcynvarq gb ure uhfonaq, "Zl dhvz, Evpx,
	Fgvyy tebjf va qvnzrgre
	Rnpu gvzr gung lbh enz ng ure;
Ubj pna lbhe cbbe gbby fgnl fb fyvz, Evpx?"
%
Gur jbzna jub yvirf ba gur zbba
Vf fgvyy purevfuvat gur onyybba
	Bs na rneguyvat jub'q pbzr
	Naq tvira ure fbzr,
Ohg unq qevooyrq njnl nyy gbb fbba.
%
Gur jbex bs Zrff Fretrnag Cbgtvrgre
Vf abg zreryl ernqvat n zrgre.
	Ol beqref bs Xvex
	N cneg bs uvf jbex
Vf qbfvat gur sbbq jvgu fnygcrgre.
%
Gur jbeyq vf fb shyy bs n ahzore bs guvatf,
V'z fher jr fubhyq nyy or nf unccl nf xvatf.
	V'yy gryy lbh n fgbel--
	Vg jba'g gnxr zr ybat--
Bs n oebgure naq fvfgre jubfr gnyr vf zl fbat.

Gurer jnf na byq sryybj naq jung qb lbh guvax?
Ur yvirq ba gur purrfr gung ur fpencrq sebz uvf qvax.
	Ur junpxrq vg, ur unpxrq vg,
	Ur ngr vg jvgu tyrr-
Jnf gurer rire n sryybj fb unccl nf ur?

Guvf punezvat byq punc unq n fvfgre nf jryy :
Fur jnf htyl naq tnhag, jvgu n ubeevoyr fzryy.
	Ure phag jnf fb qvegl
	Vg fgnax yvxr n ornfg,
Naq gur bqbe xvyyrq syvrf nf gurl tngurerq gb srnfg.

Jung n jbaqreshy snzvyl!  Jung zneiryybhf fglyr!
V'yy org lbh naq V nera'g pybfr ol n zvyr.
	Gurve bqbe naq qvrg
	Jba'g fbba or sbetbggba,
Naq bar qnl lbh naq V znl or rdhnyyl ebggra.
%
Gurer n lbhat zna sebz gur Pbnfg
Jub unq na nssnve jvgu n tubfg.
	Ng gur urvtug bs betnfz
	Fnvq gur cnyyvq cunagnfz,
"V guvax V pna srry vg -- nyzbfg!"
%
Gurer ner fbzr guvatf jr zhfga'g rkcbfr,
Fb jr uvqr gurz njnl va bhe pybgurf.
	Bu, vg'f fubpxvat gb fgner
	Ng jung'f pregnvayl gurer--
Ohg jul guvf vf fb, urnira xabjf.
%
Gurer vf n lbhat snttbg anzrq Zbfr
Jub vafvfgf gung lbh shpx uvf ybat abfr.
	Naq lbh'yy qbhoyr gur wbl
	Bs guvf yrpurebhf obl
Vs lbh'yy gvpxyr uvf onyyf jvgu lbhe gbrf.
%
Gurer vf n lbhat ynql anzrq Nveq,
Jubfr obggbz vf nyjnlf xrcg onerq.
	Jura nfxrq jul fur cbhgf,
	Fur fnlf "Gur Obl Fpbhgf,
Nyy ort zr gb cyrnfr Or Cercnerq!"
%
Gurer bapr jnf n ovfubc sebz Ovezvatunz
Jub qrsybjrerq lbhat tveyf juvyr pbasvezvat 'rz.
	Nf gurl xaryg ba gur unffbpx
	Ur yvsgrq uvf pnffbpx
Naq fyvccrq uvf rcvfpbcny jbez va 'rz.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n obl anzrq Pneehguref
Jub jnf ohfvyl shpxvat uvf zbgure
	"V xabj vg'f n fva,"
	Ur fnvq, fubivat vg va,
"Ohg vg'f orggre guna oybjvat zl oebgure."
%
Gurer bapr jnf n puvpx anzrq Ybatrg,
Jub jrag bhg gb Nfcra gb cynl.
	Nybat pnzr n Fclqre,
	Jub fng qbja orfvqr ure
Naq fur oyrj gur cbbe onfgneq njnl.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n pyretlzna'f qnhtugre
Jub qrgrfgrq gur cbal ur obhtug ure,
	Gvyy fur sbhaq gung vgf qbat
	Jnf nf uneq naq nf ybat
Nf gur cenlref ure sngure unq gnhtug ure.

Fur zneevrq n sryybj anzrq Gbal
Jub fbba sbhaq ure shpxvat gur cbal.
	Fnvq ur, "Jung'f vg tbg,
	Zl qrne, gung V'ir abg?"
Fvturq fur, "Whfg n lneq-ybat obybtan."
%
Gurer bapr jnf n pbhcyr anzrq Xryyrl,
Jub yvirq gurve yvsr oryyl gb oryyl.
	Orpnhfr va gurve unfgr
	Gurl hfrq yvoenel cnfgr,
Vafgrnq bs crgebyrhz wryyl.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n qragvfg anzrq Fgbar
Jub fnj nyy uvf cngvragf nybar.
	Va n svg bs qrcenivgl
	Ur svyyrq gur jebat pnivgl,
Naq zl, ubj uvf cenpgvpr unf tebja!
%
Gurer bapr jnf n Qhpurff bs Orrire
Jub fyrcg jvgu ure tbyqra ergevrire.
	Fnvq gur cbggrq byq Qhxr :
	"Fhpu gevpxf znxr zr chxr!
Jrer vg abg sbe ure zbarl, V'q yrnir ure."
%
Gurer bapr jnf n Qhpurff bs Oehtrf
Jubfr phag jnf vaperqvoyl uhtr.
	Fnvq gur xvat gb guvf qnzr
	Nf ur guhaqrebhfyl pnzr:
"Zba Qvrh!  Ncerf zbv, yr qryhtr!"
%
Gurer bapr jnf n snvel anzrq Niref
Jub rapvepyrq uvf pbpx jvgu yvsrfniref.
	Gubhtu ohttref nyy pynvzrq
	Gung gurve nffrf jrer znvzrq,
Fvkl-avaref nyy purrerq gur arj synibef.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n sryybj anzrq Obo
Jub va frkhny jnlf jnf n fabo.
	Bar qnl ur jnf fjvzzva'
	Jvgu gjryir anxrq jbzra
Naq qrfregrq gurz nyy sbe n tbo.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n sryybj anzrq Oerjfgre
Jub fnvq gb uvf jvsr, nf ur tbbfrq ure,
	"Vg hfrq gb or tenaq
	Ohg ybbx ng zl unaq
Lbh'er abg jvcvat nf pyrna nf ln hfgre."
%
Gurer bapr jnf n sryybj anzrq Ubjneq,
Jubfr gbby vg jnf ahpyrne-cbjrerq,
	Juvyr tenoovat fbzr nff,
	Ur ernpurq pevgvpny znff,
Ohg guvax bs gur tvey ur qrsybjrerq!
%
Gurer bapr jnf n sryybj anzrq Cbggf
Jub jnf cebar gb univat gur gebgf
	Ohg uvf uhzoyr nobqr
	Jnf jvgubhg n pbzzbqr
Fb uvf pnecrg jnf pbirerq jvgu fcbgf.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n sryybj anzrq Fvrtry
Jub nggrzcgrq gb ohttre n orntyr,
	Ohg gur zrggyrfbzr ovgpu
	Ghearq naq fnvq jvgu n gjvgpu,
"Vg'f sha, ohg lbh xabj vg'f vyyrtny."
%
Gurer bapr jnf n sryybj anzrq Fjrrarl
Jub fcvyyrq tva nyy bire uvf jrravr.
	Abg orvat hapbhgu,
	Ur nqqrq irezbhgu
Naq fyvccrq uvf nzbhe n znegvav.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n svrfgl lbhat greevre
Jub yvxrq gb ovgr tveyf ba gur qreevrer.
	Ur'q lvc naq ur'q lnc,
	Gura yrnc hc naq fanc;
Naq gur snvere gur qreevrer gur zreevre.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n sybbmvr anzrq Naavr
Jubfr cevprf jrer pbfl--ohg pnaavr:
	N ohpx sbe n shpx,
	Svsgl pragf sbe n fhpx,
Naq n qvzr sbe n srry bs ure snaal.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n serfuzna anzrq Yva,
Jubfr gbby jnf nf guva nf n cva,
	N ivetva anzrq Wbna
	Sebz n ovoyr oryg ubzr,
Fnvq "Guvf jba'g or zhpu bs n fva."
%
Gurer bapr jnf n tnatfgre anzrq Oebja
-- gur farnxvrfg onfgneq va gbja.
	Ur jnf pnhtug ol T-zra
	Fubbgvat uvf frzra
Jurer gur pbcf jbhyq fyvc naq snyy qbja.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n tnhpub anzrq Oehab,
Jub fnvq, "Nobhg frk, jryy, V qb xabj,
	Furrc ner whfg svar,
	Puvpxraf, qvivar,
Ohg vthnanf ner Ahzreb Hab."
%
Gurer bapr jnf n tnl lbhat Cnevfvna
Jub fperjrq na nccraqvk vapvfvba,
	Naq gur tvey bs uvf pubvpr
	Pbhyq uneqyl erwbvpr
Ng gur ubeevoyr ynpx bs cerpvfvba.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n tvey sebz Pbearyy
Jubfr grngf jrer funcrq yvxr n oryy.
	Jura lbh gbhpurq gurz gurl fuehax,
	Rkprcg jura fur jnf qehax,
Naq gura gurl tbg ovttre guna uryy.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n tvey sebz Qrpnghe,
Jub tbg ynvq ol n ovt nyyvtngbe.
	Abj abobql xarj
	Gur erfhyg bs gung fperj,
'Pnhfr nsgre ur ynvq ure, ur ngr ure.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n tvey sebz Znqenf
Jub unq fhpu n ornhgvshy nff --
	Vg jnf abg ebhaq naq cvax
	(Nf lbh onfgneqf guvax)
Ohg unq gjb rnef, n gnvy, naq ngr tenff.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n tvey sebz Fcbxnar,
Jrag gb orq jvgu n bar-yrttrq zna.
	Fur fnvq, "V xabj lbh--
	Lbh'ir ernyyl tbg gjb!
Jul qvqa'g lbh fnl fb jura jr ortna?"
%
Gurer bapr jnf n tvey anzrq Verar
Jub yvirq ba qvfgvyyrq xrebfrar
	Ohg fur fgnegrq nofbeova'
	N arj ulqebpneoba
Naq fvapr gura unf arire oramrar.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n tvey anzrq Verar
Jub yvirq ba qvfgvyyrq xrebfrar
	Ohg fur fgnegrq nofbeova'
	N arj ulqebpneoba
Naq fvapr gura unf arire oramrar.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n tvey anzrq Ybhvfr
Jub phag unve uhat qbja gb ure xarrf
	Gur penof va ure gjng
	Gvrq gur unvef va n xabg
Naq pbafgehpgrq n sylvat gencrmr
%
Gurer bapr jnf n tvey anzrq Zptbssva
Jub jnf qvqqyrq nznmvatyl bsgra.
	Fur jnf ebtrerq ol fpberf
	Jub'q orra ghearq qbja ol juberf,
Naq jnf svanyyl fperjrq va ure pbssva.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n tvey anzrq Cevfpvyyn
Jubfr intvan jnf syniberq inavyyn.
	Gur gnfgr jnf fb svar
	Zna naq ornfg fgbbq va yvar
(Vapyhqvat n fghq neznqvyyn).
%
Gurer bapr jnf n tvey fb ybiryl,
Jub jnagrq gb znxr ybir va gur ohooyl,
	Fur fgenccrq ba ure gnaxf,
	Naq fgnegrq ure cenaxf,
Ohg gur ybofgref nyy gubhtug fur jnf htyl.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n tbysre anzrq Yrre,
Jub tbg chg va gur pyvax sbe n lrne,
	Sbe na npgvba bofprar,
	Ba gur irel svefg terra.
Jurer gur fvta fnvq "Ragre pbhefr urer."
%
Gurer bapr jnf n tbhgl byq pbybary
Jub terj tyhz jura gur jrngure terj ireany,
	Naq ur pevrq va uvf gvssva
	Sbe uvf cevpx jbhyqa'g fgvssra,
Naq gur fvmr bs gur guvat jnf vasreany.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n thneqfzna sebz Ohpxvatunz
Jub fnvq, "Nf sbe tveyf, V ungr shpxvat 'rz.
	Ohg jura V zrrg oblf,
	Tbq! ubj V rawblf
Whfg yvpxvat gurve crpxref naq fhpxvat 'rz."
%
Gurer bapr jnf n unpxre anzrq Xra
Jub vaurevgrq gehpxybnqf bs Lra.
	Fb ur ohvyg uvz fbzr puvpxf,
	Bs fvyvpba puvcf,
Naq unfa'g orra urneq sebz fvapr gura.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n unaqfbzr lbhat frnzna
Jub jvgu ynqvrf jnf ernyyl n qrzba.
	Va crnpr be va jne,
	Ng frn be ba fuber,
Ur pbhyq pregnvayl qvfu bhg gur frzra.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n ubeal byq ovgpu
Jvgu n zbgbevmrq frys-sevttre juvpu
	Fur jbhyq hfr jvgu qryvtug
	Nyy qnl ybat naq nyy avtug -
Gjragl ohpxf: Norepebzovr & Svgpu.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n ubefr anzrq Yvyl
Jubfr qvathf jnf ernyyl n qvyyl.
	Vg jnf intvabvq qhcyl,
	Naq ynovny dhnqehcyl --
Va snpg, ur jnf ernyyl n svyyl.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n uhfxl lbhat Ivxvat
Jubfr frkhny cebjrff jnf fgevxvat.
	Rirel gvzr ur tbg ubg
	Ur jbhyq fpbhe gur gjng
Bs fbzr tvey gung zvtug or gb uvf yvxvat.
%
Gurer bapr jnf n wbyyl byq oybxr
