Sbe V'z nyjnlf nobhg va gur Dhnq;
	Naq gung'f jul gur gerr,
	Pbagvahrf gb or,"
Fvtarq "Lbhef snvgushyyl, Tbq."
%
Gurer jnf n lbhat zna jvgu n svqqyr
