	Rirel zbeavat naq avtug
	Vs vg fgbbq hc nyy evtug --
Abg n irel erznexnoyr gevpx.

Uvf jvsr unq n avpr yvggyr phag:
Vg jnf unvel, naq fbsg, naq va sebag,
	Naq jvgu guvf fur jbhyq shpx uvz,
	Gubhtu fbzrgvzrf fur'q fhpx uvz --
N punezvat, vs pbzzbacynpr, fghag.
