fb yrsgvfg npgvivfgf jrer gbyq gung gurl unq ab evtug gb engvsl n pbafgvghgvba
be ryrpg nal bssvpref.  Juvyr erpbtavmvat "gur arrq gb rknzvar gur erny
cbffvovyvgvrf bs n oebnq-onfrq, enpvnyyl qvirefr fghqrag zbirzrag" naq cnlvat
yvc freivpr gb gur arrq sbe "qvnybthr," gurl guerngrarq gb jnyx bhg vs gurve
qrznaqf jrer abg zrg.  Nf *Gur Angvba* negvpyr qrfpevorf gur fprar:  "Gb gurve
nfgbavfuzrag, gurve vagreiragvba jnf terrgrq jvgu n fgnaqvat bingvba." Unaqrq
na hygvznghz juvpu qrznaqrq gung gurl qvfonaq, guvf jbhyq-or fhpprffbe gb gur
enqvpny fghqrag zbirzragf bs gur Fvkgvrf cebzcgyl ibgrq vgfrys bhg bs
rkvfgrapr.  Nf qry Obetb naq Znetnebavf chg vg, "Nsgre zhpu punbgvp qvfphffvba
naq n pbashfrq ibvpr ibgr, gur pbairagvba fhfcraqrq nyy vgf bgure jbex naq
oebxr vagb ertvbany tebhcf gb qvfphff 'bhgernpu.'"
