	"Fher," fnvq gur onegraqre.
	"Vs," fnvq gur phfgbzre, "lbh'yy ernpu va zl evtug unaq pbng cbpxrg,
lbh'yy svaq gur zbarl sbe gur orre."
	Gur onegraqre tbg gur zbarl naq enat hc gur ovyy.
	"Lbh'ir orra irel xvaq," fnvq gur phfgbzre. "Whfg bar guvat zber.
Jurer vf gur zra'f ebbz?"
	"Hc gur fgerrg gb gur yvtug," fnvq gur onegraqre, "ghea yrsg, jnyx
gjb oybpxf, naq gurer'f n tnf fgngvba ba gur pbeare."
