n srj zbzragf, ur jnyxrq onpx bhg gb gur obng naq pyvzorq onpx va.
	Gur enoov jnf nofbyhgryl nfgbavfurq, ohg qrpvqrq abg gb zragvba
gur nccnerag zvenpyr.
	N srj zvahgrf yngre, gur cevrfg nyfb qrpvqrq gb tb nfuber sbe n
zbzrag, naq pyvzorq bhg bs gur obng, jnyxrq gb fuber, naq n srj zvahgrf
yngre pnzr onpx.
	Ol abj gur enoov jnf va terng qvfgerff naq unq ortha gb qbhog uvf
oryvrsf naq jbaqre vs gurer zvtug or fbzr inyvqvgl gb gur Puevfgvna
grnpuvatf.  Ohg ur vzzrqvngryl ernssvezrq gur snpg gung uvf snvgu JNF WHFG
NF FGEBAT nf rvgure gur cevrfg'f be gur zvavfgre'f naq qrpvqrq gung nalguvat
gurl pbhyq qb, jvgu Tbq'f uryc, ur pbhyq qb nf jryy.
	Gur enoov gura naabhaprq gung ur arrqrq eryvrs naq jbhyq jnyx gb
fuber.  Ur pyvzorq bhg bs gur obng naq jrag fgenvtug gb gur obggbz bs gur
ynxr.  Juvyr gur enoov jnf guenfuvat nobhg va gur jngre, gur cevrfg ghearq gb
gur zvavfgre naq fnvq, "Fb... qb lbh guvax jr bhtug gb gryy uvz jurer gur
ebpxf ner?"
%
Vg frrzf gung gurer jnf guvf Puevfgvna nobhg gb or guebja gb gur yvbaf.  Ur
jnf fubirq vagb gur zvqqyr bs gur neran naq gur yvba jnf eryrnfrq.  Orvat
n tbbq Puevfgvna, nf gur yvba nccebnpurq ur xaryg naq cenlrq, nfxvat Tbq sbe
sbetvirarff sbe uvf (srj) fvaf, naq orttvat gung gur yvba zvtug or qvffhnqrq
sebz rngvat uvz sbe vgf oernxsnfg.  Zhpu gb uvf qvfznl, gur yvba qvqa'g fgbc
ohg xrcg pbzvat, trggvat snfgre naq snfgre, abj nyzbfg ehaavat, fb gur
Puevfgvna gbbx bss gbb.  Gurer gurl jrer, ehaavat nebhaq naq nebhaq gur neran,
gur yvba trggvat pybfre naq gur Puevfgvna cenlvat uneqre naq uneqre orgjrra
tnfcf sbe oerngu.  Gur yvbaf oerngu jnf abj ubg hcba uvf urryf naq ur pbhyq
rira srry qebcyrgf bs gur yvbaf fnyvin fcynfuvat ba uvf oner srrg.  Fb ur
chyyrq bhg nyy gur fgbcf, cebzvfvat Tbq gung vs gur yvba jvyy bayl fcner uvz,
ur jvyy qribgr gur erfg bs uvf yvsr gb fcernqvat gur Puevfgvna snvgu,
sbefnxvat nyy grzcgngvba naq cbffrffvbaf.  Fhqqrayl ur ab ybatre sryg gur
yvbaf oerngu, ab ybatre urneq gur terng ornfg'f faneyf pybfr oruvaq uvz.
Fybjvat gb n fgbc, ur ghearq nebhaq naq fnj gur yvba ba vgf xarrf, rlrf ebyyrq
hcjneq, cnjf uryq gbtrgure.  Gur yvba nccrnerq gb or zhggrevat fbzrguvat fb
gur Puevfgvna nccebnpurq hagvy ur pbhyq znxr bhg jung gur yvba jnf fnlvat.

"Qrne Ybeq, sbe jung V nz nobhg gb erprvir..."
%
... vg fgvyy erznvaf gehr gung nf n frg bs pbtavgvir oryvrsf nobhg gur
rkvfgrapr bs Tbq va nal erpbtavmnoyr frafr pbagvahbhf jvgu gur terng
flfgrzf bs gur cnfg, eryvtvbhf qbpgevarf pbafgvghgr n fcrphyngvir
ulcbgurfvf bs na rkgerzryl ybj beqre bs cebonovyvgl.
