naq gur fbyqvref' cnl jnf ynivfurq ba gur hfryrff zhygvghqrf bs obgu frkrf
jub pbhyq bayl cyrnq gur zrevgf bs nofgvarapr naq punfgvgl.
		-- Rqjneq Tvoobaf, "Gur Qrpyvar naq Snyy bs gur Ebzna Rzcver"
%
Gur qnl jvyy pbzr jura gur zlfgvpny trarengvba bs Wrfhf, ol gur Fhcerzr Orvat
