10 Ernfbaf Jul n Orre vf Orggre Guna n Zna:

	 (1) N orre ARIRE yrnirf gur gbvyrg frng hc.
	 (2) N orre ynfgf ybatre guna frira frpbaqf.
	 (3) N orre qbrfa'g jnag gb jngpu ceb jerfgyvat.
	 (4) N orre jba'g rkcrpg lbh gb pbbx qvaare jura lbh'er abg uhatel.
	 (5) N orre jvyy arire yrnir qvegl fbpxf ba gur sybbe.
	 (6) N orre qbrfa'g zvaq jura lbhe zbgure ivfvgf.
	 (7) N orre qbrf nf znal puberf nf n zna, jvgu n YBG yrff pbzcynvavat.
	 (8) N orre jba'g yrnir lbh sbe n lbhatre jbzna.
	 (9) N orre jba'g yrnir lbh sbe n lbhatre zna rvgure.
	(10) N orre jba'g grnfr lbh orpnhfr lbh bapr yvxrq Oneel Znavybj.
%
10 Ernfbaf Jul n Orre vf Orggre Guna n Zna:

	 (1) N orre jvyy arire vaivgr sevraqf ubzr sbe qvaare jvgubhg pnyyvat.
	 (2) N orre jba'g guvax yrff bs lbh vs lbh pna'g anzr gur Fgrryref'
	     dhnegreonpx.
