10 Ernfbaf Jul n Orre vf Orggre Guna n Zna:

	 (1) Univat n orre pna'g znxr lbh certanag.
	 (2) N orre qbrfa'g jbhyqa'g genqr lbh va ba n fcbegf pne.
	 (3) Vs n orre qvq unir n fcbegf pne, vg jbhyqa'g ybir vg zber guna lbh.
	 (4) N orre qbrfa'g jnag gb tb bhg nybar jvgu gur bgure orref.
	 (5) N orre jbhyqa'g jnfgr vgf zbarl ba Cynlorre zntnmvar.
	 (6) Lbh qba'g unir gb jbeel nobhg trggvat NVQF sebz n ovfrkhny orre.
	 (7) N orre jba'g fjvgpu gur GI punaary.
	 (8) N orre qbrfa'g faber.
