V pbhyqa'g nfx sbe zber,
Fur'f qrns naq qhzo naq bire-frkrq,
Naq bjaf n yvdhbe fgber.
%
Vs V unq n cravf V'q jrne vg bhgfvqr,
Va pnsrf naq pne ybgf, jvgu cbzc naq jvgu cevqr.
Vs V unq n cravf V'q cnzcre vg cebcre
V'q fgnl va gur gho naq hfr zr nf gur fgbccre.
Vs V unq n cravf V'q gnxr vg gb cnegvrf
Fgergpu vg naq fgebxr vg naq fubir vg ng fznegvrf.
V'q gnxr vg gb crg fubjf naq grnpu vg gb fgnl.
V'q fghss vg va ghexrlf ba Gunaxftvivat Qnl.

V'q eviny zl ohqqvrf va fcbegfpnef naq fgvpx fuvsgf.
