Naq rireljurer gung Znel jrag, gur ynzo jnf fher gb tb.
Vg sbyybjrq ure guebhtu enva be fabj, yvtugavat, fyrrg be unvy.
Vg srgpurq gur riravat cncre, ure fyvccref, naq gur znvy.
Fur arire unq n zbzrag'f crnpr; gur ynzo jnf nyjnlf ba ure urryf,
Naq ba ure srrg vgf urnq jbhyq erfg, juvyr fur ngr ure zrnyf.
Vg sbyybjrq ure gb fpubby bar qnl, gur qribgvba arire raqrq.
Gur ynzo jnygmrq vagb ure uvfgbel pynff naq Znel tbg fhfcraqrq.
