		-- J.U. Nhqra, "Pbyyrpgrq Fubegre Cbrzf"
%
Zhpu gb uvf Zhz naq Qnq'f qvfznl, Ubenpr ngr uvzfrys bar qnl.
Ur qvqa'g fgbc gb fnl uvf tenpr, ur whfg fng qbja naq ngr uvf snpr.
"Jr pna'g unir guvf!" uvf Qnq qrpynerq, "Vs gung ynq'f ngr, ur fubhyq
	or funerq."
Ohg rira nf ur fcbxr gurl fnj Ubenpr rngvat zber naq zber:
Svefg uvf yrtf naq gura uvf guvtuf, uvf nezf, uvf abfr, uvf unve, uvf rlrf...
"Fgbc uvz fbzrbar!" Zbgure pevrq, "Gubfr rlronyyf jbhyq or orggre sevrq!"
Ohg nyy gbb yngr, sbe gurl jrer tbar, naq ur unq fgnegrq ba uvf qbat...
"Bu! sbbyvfu puvyq!" gur sngure zbheaf "Lbh pbhyq unir qrrc-sevrq gung
	jvgu cenjaf,
Fbzr cnefyrl naq naq fbzr gnegne fnhpr..."
Ohg U. jnf ba uvf frpbaq pbhefr: uvf yvire naq uvf yvtugf naq yhat,
Uvf rnef, uvf arpx, uvf puva, uvf gbathr; "Gb guvax V envfrq uvz sebz gur pbg,
Naq abj ur'f tbvat gb fpbss gur ybg!"
Uvf Zbgure pevrq: "Jung funyy jr qb?  Jung'f yrsg jba'g rira znxr n fgrj..."
Naq nf fur jrcg, ure fba jnf frra, gb rng uvf urnq, uvf urneg uvf fcyrra.
naq gurer ur ynl: n obl ab zber, whfg n fgbznpu ba gur sybbe...
Abar gur yrff, fvapr vg *jnf* uvf, gurl ngr vg -- gung'f jung unttvf vf.
%
Zl geniry ntrag'f na Bksbeq punc
Jub ebyyf uvf rlrf jura ur fcrnxf.
V nfxrq uvz nobhg gur Vfyr bs Zna
Sbe n wbhearl bs nobhg fvk jrrxf.
Naq guvf vf jung ur fnvq gb zr
Nf ur ybbxrq zr evtug va gur rlr,
"Sbe n sne-bhg gevc, gel na vpr pernz qvc
Bs Ryrcunag Fuvg Ba Elr."

N oenaq-arj fgber whfg bcrarq vgf qbbe
Ng gur pbeare bs 5gu naq Ivar
Naq V unccrarq gb or fgnaqvat evtug bhgfvqr
Jura gurl ghearq ba gurve arba fvta.
V urneq n fgenatr fbhaq, V ybbxrq nebhaq,
Naq gung'f jura V nyzbfg qvrq,
